 which makes it easier for importers and retailers to position.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">The third strength is presentation. Bamboo gives the organizer a warmer and more natural look than plastic or metal storage, which helps it fit premium homeware and hospitality-oriented lines.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">For private label projects, the product is also easy to adapt. Size, drawer front style, finish, logo and packaging can all be adjusted according to the target channel.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 24px; background: #fffdf8; border: 1px solid #eadfce;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 30px; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #3d2d20;\">Product Information<\/h2>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #5a4938;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Product Name:<\/strong> Custom Bamboo Countertop Organizer with Drawer<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Material:<\/strong> Bamboo or other wood options based on project needs<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Structure:<\/strong> Open shelf + pull-out drawer + countertop storage rack<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Usage:<\/strong> Kitchen counter storage, coffee station organization, pantry storage, bathroom or vanity organization<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Style:<\/strong> Freestanding countertop organizer<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Finish:<\/strong> Natural finish, stained finish or customized surface treatment<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Logo:<\/strong> Laser engraving, screen printing, UV print or label application<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Size:<\/strong> Standard size or custom dimensions<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Packaging:<\/strong> Export carton, brown box, color box or customized retail packaging<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>MOQ:<\/strong> Based on size, finish, logo method and packaging det