ive to plastic storage organizers.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">Private label buyers who need custom logo, custom size and custom packaging support.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"padding: 26px; background: #efe6d8; border: 1px solid #d9c7ab;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 30px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #3d2d20;\">FAQ<\/h2>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Can you customize the size of the organizer?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">Yes. We can adjust the overall width, height, shelf depth and drawer size based on your target market and usage needs.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Can the drawer and shelf layout be changed?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">Yes. The structure can be discussed according to the items you want to store, such as coffee accessories, pantry items, kitchen tools or bathroom products.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Can you add our logo?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">Yes. We usually support laser engraving, printing, UV logo or label application depending on the final style and budget.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Is this only for kitchen use?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">No. Although it works very well in kitchens and coffee stations, it can also be used for pantry, vanity, bathroom or general countertop organization projects.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Can you provide custom packaging for retail or export orders?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">Yes. We can provide standard export packaging as well as custom color box, insert 