mall bottles and beauty items in a cleaner, more elevated way. The round base, raised center platform, and upper shelf create layered visual space without making the countertop feel crowded.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">For importers and brand owners, this type of structure works well because it feels decorative but remains practical. It can be used for perfume, skincare, essential oils, makeup items, or curated gift sets.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Why This Product Works for B2B Buyers<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">Display products sell differently from simple storage products. Buyers usually want something that can improve presentation, support styling, and help products stand out in store photos, catalog shots, and shelf displays.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This design is useful because it crosses several markets at once. It can fit perfume display, cosmetic organizer, vanity storage, retail counter display, and gift-ready homeware collections.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">It also works well for brands that want a natural wood look instead of acrylic or metal. That makes it especially suitable for clean beauty, fragrance, boutique, and lifestyle brands.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Information<\/h2>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #4e4338;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Product Type:<\/strong> Wooden perfume display stand \/ countertop cosmetic organizer \/ vanity display stand<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Main Material:<\/strong> Solid wood or custom wood options<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Structure:<\/st