 color: #2f2822;\">Product Overview<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This acacia wood magnetic knife block is designed to store kitchen knives in a cleaner and more flexible way than a traditional slot block. The hidden magnetic structure keeps knives visible, easy to access, and neatly presented on the countertop.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">For importers and brand buyers, this product offers both function and shelf appeal. It works well as a standalone kitchen item, a bundled accessory, or a premium private label houseware product.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Why This Product Works for B2B Buyers<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">Knife storage is a practical category, but presentation matters. A wooden magnetic knife block looks more premium than plastic holders and gives buyers a more modern alternative to fixed-slot knife blocks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This format also helps brand owners build a stronger kitchen collection. It pairs naturally with cutting boards, utensil holders, trays, and other wooden kitchen accessories.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">For wholesalers and retailers, the selling points are easy to understand. Strong magnets, visible blade storage, and a stable countertop base are clear benefits that support both online and offline sales.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Information<\/h2>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #4e4338;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Product Type:<\/strong> Magnetic knife block \/ wooden magnetic knife holder \/ countertop knife storage block<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Main Material:<\/strong> Acacia wood or other custom wood options<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Structure:<\/strong> Freestanding countertop block with hidden magnetic panel and stable base<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Use:<\/strong> Kitchen knife storage, countertop display, kitchen organization<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Customization:<\/strong> Logo, size, finish, wood species, packaging, and structure details<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>Packaging:<\/strong> Bulk export packing, inner box, and master carton available<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Highlights<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Strong hidden magnetic support.<\/strong> The block is designed to hold kitchen knives securely while keeping blades visible and easy to reach.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Natural acacia wood appearance.<\/strong> The wood grain gives the product a warm and premium look that fits modern kitchen collections and gift-oriented retail lines.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Countertop-friendly design.<\/strong> The upright structure helps save drawer space and creates a cleaner presentation in the kitchen.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Stable base for daily use.<\/strong> The bottom structure is important for real kitchen use, especially for buyers who want both appearance and practicality.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\"><strong>OEM and ODM flexibility.<\/strong> The design can be developed with different wood tones, dimensions, logo methods, and packaging styles based on your target market.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Ideal For<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This product is suitable for kitchenware brands, homeware importers, wholesalers, retailers, hotel supply companies, and private label buyers.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">It also works well for companies building coordinated wooden kitchen collections, especially those already selling cutting boards, utensil holders, trays, and knife accessories.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #efe4d3; border: 1px solid #dcc7ab; padding: 32px 28px; margin: 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">FAQ &amp; CTA<\/h2>\n<div style=\"margin: 0 0 26px 0;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can you add our logo?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. We can support laser engraving, printed branding, or other suitable logo methods depending on the wood finish and project requirement.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can the size or shape be customized?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. We can discuss custom dimensions, panel width, base structure, and overall format based on your market positioning.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can you use other wood materials?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. Acacia is a strong option, but we can also review other wood species depending on your budget, color preference, and target market.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Is this suitable for wholesale and export projects?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. This product is developed for bulk orders, OEM branding, and export packaging, not only for single retail sales.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\"><strong>Can you provide custom packaging?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. We can support inner box, gift box, barcode label, and export carton solutions according to your sales channel.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"border-top: 1px solid