 0; color: #5a4e44;\">A practical wooden comment box for feedback collection, ballot use, donation campaigns, and branded display projects.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 34px 0; color: #5a4e44;\">Designed for B2B buyers who need a secure, presentable, and easy-to-customize box for retail, hospitality, office, school, church, and event use.<\/p>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Overview<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This wooden suggestion box with lock combines function and presentation in one compact design. It includes a ballot slot, lockable lid, top sign holder, chalkboard front, and side storage for markers or accessories.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">For importers and brand buyers, this structure is useful because it works across multiple use cases without changing the core shape. It can be positioned as a feedback box, comment card box, ballot box, donation box, or event collection box.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Why This Product Works for B2B Buyers<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">The product is easy to adapt for different markets. A hospitality buyer may use it for guest feedback, a retailer may use it for customer comments, and an event supplier may position it as a ballot or card collection box.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">The front chalkboard area adds merchandising value. Buyers can change the message by season, store campaign, or brand event without changing the box itself.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">The lockable structure also makes the item more suitable for commercial settings where privacy, cash handling, voting, or controlled access matters.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Information<\/h2>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #4e4338;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Product Type:<\/strong> Wooden suggestion box \/ comment box \/ ballot box \/ donation box<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Main Material:<\/strong> Solid wood, pine or other custom wood options available<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Structure:<\/strong> Lockable top lid with slot, front chalkboard panel, sign holder, side pen holder<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Installation:<\/strong> Wall mounted or countertop display<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0;\"><strong>Accessories:<\/strong> Keys, markers, eraser, screws and wall plugs can be included<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>Customization:<\/strong> Logo, color, wording, package, insert card design, and construction details<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Product Highlights<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Lockable wooden box structure.<\/strong> Suitable for collecting suggestions, ballots, donation slips, forms, notes, or cards in a more secure way.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Front writable chalkboard panel.<\/strong> Easy for end users to change messages such as comments, feedback, vote here, donation, or event instructions.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Top card display holder.<\/strong> Helps buyers present campaign cards, floral signs, instruction cards, store notices, or branded inserts.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Side pen and accessory storage.<\/strong> Useful for markers, pens, or erasers, which makes the product more complete for real commercial use.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\"><strong>OEM and ODM flexibility.<\/strong> The same structure can be developed for restaurant feedback, hotel guest comments, office voting, church donation use, or event collection.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf2; border: 1px solid #e7dccb; padding: 28px 28px; margin: 0 0 34px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">Ideal For<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This product is a good fit for wholesalers, importers, hospitality suppliers, office product distributors, church supply buyers, wedding and event brands, and retail chains.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0;\">It also works well for brands looking for a custom wooden comment box, lockable ballot box, or countertop donation box with a more natural and giftable appearance than acrylic or metal options.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #efe4d3; border: 1px solid #dcc7ab; padding: 32px 28px; margin: 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #2f2822;\">FAQ &amp; Inquiry<\/h2>\n<div style=\"margin: 0 0 26px 0;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can you add our logo?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. We can support laser engraving, printed logo, or customized front message depending on the project.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can the box be wall mounted?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. This design can be supplied for countertop use, wall mounting, or both, depending on your requirement.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\"><strong>Can we change the color or wood type?<\/strong><br \/>\nYes. Natural wood, painted finishes, stained colors, and selected wood options can be discussed based on volume and target market.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 22px; margi