6px 24px; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #3f372f; font-weight: bold;\">Short Description<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This bamboo spa gift set tray is designed for wholesale buyers, gift set brands, hotel suppliers and wellness projects that need a natural and premium presentation base. The tray includes a divided bamboo tray, bamboo bowls and bamboo spoons, creating a clean and coordinated look for bath salt gift sets, spa kits and custom self care collections.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0;\">It is a good choice for brands looking for reusable packaging, boutique spa presentation and custom bamboo tray solutions with logo, size and packaging options.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #fffdf8; border: 1px solid #e6dac8; padding: 26px 24px; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #3f372f; font-weight: bold;\">Product Overview<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">If you are sourcing a <strong style=\"color: #4a4036;\">bamboo spa gift set tray<\/strong> for a retail brand, private label project or hotel spa program, this style gives you a strong balance of presentation and practicality. The divided tray structure helps separate bowls, spoons, bath salts, dried flowers, sachets or beauty accessories in a way that looks organized, premium and easy to merchandise.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">Compared with ordinary paper inserts or disposable plastic trays, a bamboo tray creates a warmer and more upscale first impression. For B2B buyers, that matters. The product looks more gift ready on shelf, photographs better for online sales, and supports a more natural wellness image for spa and self care collections.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This product works especially well for <strong style=\"color: #4a4036;\">bath salt gift set tray<\/strong>, <strong style=\"color: #4a4036;\">wellness gift tray<\/strong>, pedicure presentation tray, salon display tray and <strong style=\"color: #4a4036;\">hotel spa amenity tray<\/strong> projects. Buyers can use the tray as a ready made presentation base or develop a fully customized set with their own filling materials and retail packaging.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">The sample shown uses a rectangular bamboo tray with multiple bamboo bowls and small bamboo spoons. The tray style is suitable for bath salts, scrub samples, cream samples, dried petals, soap pieces, spa tablets and small beauty accessories. It is not positioned as a large capacity organizer. It is positioned as a premium display and gift presentation tray for curated spa sets.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">For importers and brand owners, one important advantage is reusability. After the spa contents are used, the bamboo tray can still be kept for bathroom countertop storage, vanity display, hotel amenity organization or salon presentation. That added reuse value helps the final set feel more premium and more worth keeping.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">This is also a practical item for OEM and ODM development. We can adjust tray size, compartment layout, bowl size, spoon style, surface finish, logo method and gift box packaging according to your target market. If you are building a collection for boutique retail, spa chain stores, hotel welcome gifts, holiday gifting or wellness subscription projects, this tray provides a flexible bamboo base that can be adapted to many product combinations.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px 0;\">Because the visual language is natural, clean and neutral, the design fits many brand directions. It can support minimalist wellness brands, floral spa collections, lavender themed gift sets, salon treatment kits and natural bath care ranges. For wholesalers, thi