d; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 9px 15px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 18px;\">OEM and Wholesale Supplier<\/div>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 46px; line-height: 1.25; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold;\">Custom Wooden Pet Memorial Box with Photo Frame<\/h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #665545;\">A warm and display friendly wooden pet memorial box designed for brands, importers, distributors and online sellers.<br \/>\nThis photo frame pet ashes box combines keepsake storage with visual memorial value, making it easier to position in<br \/>\npet memorial collections, sympathy gift lines and private label programs.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"padding: 42px;\">\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.25; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold;\">Short Description<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">This custom wooden pet memorial box is developed for wholesale buyers who need a meaningful and customizable memorial product.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">The front photo frame gives the product a warmer and more personal look, while the box body offers practical space for ashes,<br \/>\ncollars, tags, fur clippings or other keepsakes.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">Size, color, logo, structure and packaging can all be adjusted according to your market needs, price target and brand style.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.25; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold;\">Detailed Description<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">A good memorial product should feel respectful, warm and easy to understand at first glance. That is why this design works so well.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">It combines a clean wooden box with a visible photo frame front, so the product feels more personal than a plain urn box<br \/>\nand easier to present as part of a premium memorial collection.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">For B2B buyers, this matters. A product with both display value and storage function is usually easier to sell across pet memorial,<br \/>\nsympathy gift and remembrance categories.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">This style can work as a dog memorial box, cat memorial box, wood pet urn, photo frame pet urn or pet keepsake box.<br \/>\nThat flexibility makes it useful for brands building a broader memorial product line.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">From a sourcing point of view, it is also a practical model. Buyers can adjust box size, frame proportion, wood tone,<br \/>\nopening structure, inside layout, logo method and finish direction.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">The front frame area gives more room for branding as well. It can be matched with engraved wording, logo plate,<br \/>\nprinted logo or other memorial details based on your project.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">Packaging is based on buyer requirements. We can discuss retail gift box packing, mail order solutions, barcode labels,<br \/>\ninsert cards, thank you cards and outer carton specifications according to your channel needs.<\/p>\n<div style=\"background: #f3eadf; border-left: 5px solid #b18962; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-top: 20px;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 23px; line-height: 1.95; color: #55473b;\">In simple terms, this is not just a wooden box. It is a flexible memorial product that combines emotional presentation,<br \/>\npractical storage and OEM customization value in one design.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #fcf8f2; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 24px 22px;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836;\">Why It Sells Better<\/h3>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">The photo display plus keepsake storage concept gives buyers a stronger product story than a plain box,<br \/>\nwhich helps the item work better in memorial and sympathy related collections.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcf8f2; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 24px 22px;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836;\">What Can Be Customized<\/h3>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Size, wood color, logo method, inside layout, wording plate and customer defined packaging can all be adjusted<br \/>\nfor different markets.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcf8f2; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 24px 22px;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836;\">Suitable Sales Channels<\/h3>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Ideal for wholesalers, distributors, pet memorial brands, gift companies, cross border sellers and private label buyers.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcf8f2; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 24px 22px;\">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836;\">Packaging Note<\/h3>\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Packaging is customer defined. We can follow your required packing style for retail, gifting, e commerce or wholesale shipment.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 20px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.25; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold;\">Product Highlights<\/h2>\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;\">\n<div style=\"font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Photo Frame Design<\/div>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Adds visual memorial value and makes the product feel warmer than a standard ashes box.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;\">\n<div style=\"font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Multiple Market Uses<\/div>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Suitable for dog memorial, cat memorial, pet ashes storage and keepsake gift collections.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;\">\n<div style=\"font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;\">OEM Friendly<\/div>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">Easy to customize for different sizes, finishes, logos and packaging requirements.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;\">\n<div style=\"font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.35; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;\">B2B Ready<\/div>\n<div style=\"font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.9; color: #5b4d40;\">A practical item for importers, memorial brands, distributors and wholesale online sellers.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 20px; font-family: Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.25; color: #5d4836; font-weight: bold;\">FAQ<\/h2>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Can you make this pet memorial box in different sizes<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. Size customization is one of the most common requests for this product. Some buyers prefer a compact keepsake version,<br \/>\nwhile others need a larger wooden pet urn style box. We can develop the size according to your target market.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Can the color be changed<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. Different wood tones and finish directions can be discussed during sampling. Natural wood style,<br \/>\ndarker walnut tone and other customized finishes are all possible depending on your project.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Do you offer logo customization<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. For wholesale and private label buyers, logo customization can usually be done by laser engraving,<br \/>\nmetal plate, printed logo or other suitable methods based on your design and quantity.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Is this product suitable for both dogs and cats<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. This design works well for dog memorial and cat memorial collections. Many buyers use it as a general pet memorial box<br \/>\nso it can fit multiple pet categories.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Can the inside structure be customized<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. If you need a different inside layout, divider concept or storage structure, we can review it during sample development<br \/>\nand adjust it according to your intended use.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Do you support custom packaging<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. Packaging is based on buyer requirements. If you already have a gift box idea, barcode request,<br \/>\ninsert card or outer carton standard, we can discuss it together with the product specification.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Is this a good item for private label programs<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3d4;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.95; color: #5b4d40;\">Yes. This product is suitable for private label because the memorial theme is clear, the front frame area is visually attractive<br \/>\nand the overall design gives enough space for custom branding and packaging upgrades.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/details>\n<details style=\"background: #fffaf4; border: 1px solid #eadfce; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<summary style=\"cursor: pointer; padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: bold; color: #5a4738;\">Can I start with samples before placing a bulk order<\/summary>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 24px 22px; border-top: 1px solid #eee3