ttps:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=6175"},"modified":"2026-03-17T12:08:04","modified_gmt":"2026-03-17T12:08:04","slug":"custom-bamboo-rattan-serving-tray-set","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/product\/custom-bamboo-rattan-serving-tray-set\/","title":{"rendered":"Custom Bamboo Rattan Serving Tray Set"},"content":{"rendered":"<section style=\"max-width: 920px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2f2f2f; line-height: 1.8;\">\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 18px; padding: 36px 32px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 36px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #222;\">Custom Bamboo Rattan Serving Tray Set<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #5f5a54; margin: 0 0 14px;\">Our custom bamboo rattan serving tray set combines a clean bamboo frame with a woven center panel for a natural and modern look.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #5f5a54; margin: 0;\">Available in round and rectangular designs, this tray set is suitable for wholesalers, hotel suppliers, retailers and private label brands looking for decorative yet practical serving and display trays.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #222;\">Product Description<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; color: #666; margin: 0;\">Designed for B2B buyers who need a tray collection that feels natural, looks premium and works across multiple sales channels.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Natural Style with Strong Market Appeal<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">This bamboo rattan serving tray set is designed for buyers who want a product that feels warm, natural and easy to match with different interior styles.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">The bamboo frame gives the tray a clean structure, while the woven center panel adds texture and visual interest. The result is a tray set that looks decorative, but still remains highly practical for daily use.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Round and Rectangular Designs in One Collection<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">This collection includes both round and rectangular tray shapes.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">For wholesalers and brand owners, that creates a stronger product line. Instead of offering only one style, you can build a more complete collection for your catalog, website or retail program.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">The mixed shape option also gives buyers more flexibility for different room settings and product positioning.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Practical for Daily Use<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">The raised edge helps keep cups, bottles, snacks, sachets and small accessories in place.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">Open side handles make the trays easier to carry, which is useful for serving, room setup and display use.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">The nesting structure also helps save storage space, making the set more convenient for packing, shipping and warehouse management.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Suitable for Multiple Applications<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">This tray set can be used in many different sales channels and project types.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">It works well as a coffee tray, breakfast tray, bathroom amenity tray, hotel welcome tray, countertop organizer tray or tabletop display tray.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">Because of its natural look, it fits home decor brands, hotel suppliers, resort projects, gift companies and lifestyle retailers.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Good Choice for Hotel and Home Collections<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">For hospitality buyers, this tray can be used in guest rooms, bathroom counters, coffee corners and welcome setups.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">For homeware brands, it offers a simple but attractive item that fits modern natural, boho, coastal and Japandi style collections.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">This wider usage helps buyers market the product more easily in different countries and sales channels.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">OEM and ODM Customization<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">We support OEM and ODM service for B2B buyers.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">Size, shape, tray depth, logo method and finish can be adjusted according to your target market and project needs.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">Custom logo options can include laser engraving, screen printing, sticker label or hang tag solutions.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">Packaging is buyer defined and can be discussed based on your order requirements.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: #fcfaf7; border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 27px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Why This Product Works for Wholesale<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">Compared with a plain wooden tray, this bamboo rattan tray set offers more texture and stronger visual appeal.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">Compared with a fully woven tray, it keeps a cleaner structure that many modern buyers prefer.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">This balance between decoration and function makes it a practical option for importers, wholesalers and private label brands looking for a product with broad market appeal.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fcfaf7 0%, #f7f2ea 100%); border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 30px; margin-bottom: 48px;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Wholesale Inquiry<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #555;\">If you are looking for a custom bamboo rattan serving tray supplier, we can support your project with sampling, customization and bulk production.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">Send us your target size, quantity, logo request and packaging details, and we will check the most suitable solution for your market.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #222;\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; color: #666; margin: 0;\">Common questions from wholesalers, retailers, hotel buyers and private label customers.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; background: #fcfaf7;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 25px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">What material is this tray made of<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">This style is presented as a bamboo tray with a woven center panel. If you need material details confirmed for sampling or quotation, we can check the exact construction with you before production.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; background: #fcfaf7;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 25px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Do you offer both round and rectangular shapes<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">Yes. This product can be developed in round and rectangular versions, and tray sets in multiple sizes are also possible for wholesale programs.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; background: #fcfaf7;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 25px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Can you add our logo on the tray<\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; margin: 0; color: #555;\">Yes. We support custom logo service for B2B orders. Common options include laser engraving, screen printing, sticker label and hang tag.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #e8e1d8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; background: #fcfaf7;\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 25px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #222;\">Is this tray suitable for hotel projects<\/h3>\n<p style=\"