suitable for disposable face towels, tissue packs and hand towel box style applications, depending on the final inner dimension.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5197\" data-end=\"5320\">The overall style is clean and modern, which makes it suitable for home, hotel, spa, salon and personal care product lines.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"5322\" data-end=\"5325\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"16d9p6j\" data-start=\"5327\" data-end=\"5353\">Material and Appearance<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"5355\" data-end=\"5433\">The natural bamboo look gives the holder a warm, tidy and upgraded appearance.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5435\" data-end=\"5571\">This style works especially well in bathroom and vanity collections where customers prefer neutral, natural materials and simple shapes.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5573\" data-end=\"5669\">The box is designed to improve product presentation while keeping the countertop more organized.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5671\" data-end=\"5808\">For brands selling bathroom organizers or tissue storage products, this design fits easily into modern retail and online catalog systems.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"5810\" data-end=\"5813\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"bn7wp\" data-start=\"5815\" data-end=\"5832\">Functional Use<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"5834\" data-end=\"5942\">The holder is designed for dry use on bathroom countertops, vanities, dressing tables and guest room spaces.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5944\" data-end=\"6046\">The front window style opening helps show the remaining quantity and supports a cleaner daily display.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6048\" data-end=\"6107\">The top access structure is practical for quick dispensing.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6109\" data-end=\"6234\">For B2B clients, this gives the product wider usability across home storage, spa accessories and hospitality supply programs.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"6236\" data-end=\"6239\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"uqcdzq\" data-start=\"6241\" data-end=\"6273\">Custom Development for Brands<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"6275\" data-end