p>\n<p data-start=\"6545\" data-end=\"6613\">It also works well for buyers building a bamboo bathroom collection.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6624\" data-end=\"6694\"><strong data-start=\"6624\" data-end=\"6694\">Can this product be sold together with other bamboo bathroom items<\/strong><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6696\" data-end=\"6739\">Yes. That is actually one of its strengths.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6741\" data-end=\"6843\">It matches well with bamboo trays, tissue box covers, bathroom organizers, and other storage products.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6741\" data-end=\"6843\">\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This bamboo toilet paper storage box with lid is designed for wholesalers, importers, and homeware brands looking for a clean and practical bathroom storage product. Its rectangular shape, removable lid, and natural bamboo finish make it suitable for modern bathroom collections, private label projects, and compact storage lines.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":6040,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[65],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-6035","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-wooden-bathroom-organizer","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"shipping-taxable","11":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/6035","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6035"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6040"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6035"}],"wp:term":[{