s, jewelry or gift sets, we can discuss the inner structure based on your packing needs.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5427\" data-end=\"5764\"><strong data-start=\"5427\" data-end=\"5471\">4. What is the MOQ for wholesale orders?<\/strong><br data-start=\"5471\" data-end=\"5474\" \/>MOQ depends on the box size, material, customization details and packing method. For standard styles, the MOQ is usually more friendly. For fully customized projects, the quantity may be higher. The best way is to send us your size and logo request first, then we can quote more accurately.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5766\" data-end=\"6098\"><strong data-start=\"5766\" data-end=\"5824\">5. Can this blank box be finished in different styles?<\/strong><br data-start=\"5824\" data-end=\"5827\" \/>Yes. That is one of the reasons many buyers choose this style. The same basic box can be kept natural, painted, stained, printed or upgraded with custom hardware. If you are also planning a decorative or vintage style collection, we can discuss those finishes separately.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6100\" data-end=\"6328\"><strong data-start=\"6100\" data-end=\"6153\">6. Do you provide samples before bulk production?<\/strong><br data-start=\"6153\" data-end=\"6156\" \/>Yes, normally we can arrange a sample first. This is especially useful if you need to check size, surface finish, logo position or insert fit before placing the bulk order.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6330\" data-end=\"6631\"><strong data-start=\"6330\" data-end=\"6374\">7. How do you pack the boxes for export?<\/strong><br data-start=\"6374\" data-end=\"6377\" \/>We can arrange standard export carton packing, and if needed we can also discuss individual box protection, inner polybag, paper wrap, barcode labels or custom retail packaging. Packing can be adjusted according to your shipping method and sales channel.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6633\" data-end=\"6945\"><strong data-start=\"6633\" data-end=\"6705\">8. Is this a good product for distributors and private label buyers?<\/strong><br data-start=\"6705\" data-end=\"6708\" \/>Yes. This style is suitable for distributors because it is a broad-use product, and it is also suitable for private label buyers because it can be customized into different packaging programs without changing the core structure too much.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Looking for blank wooden boxes wholesale for your brand, retail line or packaging project? Our unfinished wooden boxes with hinged lids are designed for bulk orders and OEM customization. They are suitable for gift packaging, craft kits, keepsake storage, promotional sets and personalized branding with laser logo, UV printing, inserts and custom sizes.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":6016,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[70,66],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-6008","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-custom-wooden-packaging-box","7":"product_cat-wooden-gift-box","9":"last","10":"instock","11":"shipping-taxable","12":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/6008","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6008"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6016"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6008"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=6008"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=6008"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=6008"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}},{"id":6001,"date":"2026-03-09T11:01:34","date_gmt":"2026-03-09T11:01:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=6001"},"modified":"2026-03-09T11:01:34","modified_gmt":"2026-03-09T11:01:34","slug":"small-wooden-box-with-lid","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/product\/small-wooden-box-with-lid\/","title":{"rendered":"Custom Small Wooden Box with Lid for Gift Packaging and Craft Projects"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3 data-section-id=\"18730fm\" data-start=\"1638\" data-end=\"1692\">Custom Small Wooden Box with Lid for B2B Packaging<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1693\" data-end=\"2010\">This small wooden box with lid is developed for importers, wholesalers, private label brands, and gift packaging buyers who need a clean and natural wood packaging solution. Its compact rectangular shape and sliding lid structure make it practical for small products, branded kits, and promotional packaging programs.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"3i7l3h\" data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2071\">Sliding Lid Structure for Simple and Clean Presentation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2072\" data-end=\"2424\">Compared with more complex hinged designs, this wooden box with lid uses a sliding top structure that keeps the appearance neat and modern. It is easy to open, easy to close, and suitable for repeat production. The box works well for small accessories, cards, jewelry, tea items, keepsakes, and other compact products that need a reusable wood package.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"p19k26\" data-start=\"2426\" data-end=\"2486\">Suitable for Wooden Craft Boxes and Wooden Present Boxes<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2487\" data-end=\"2896\">For customers sourcing wooden craft boxes or wooden present boxes, this model offers a flexible base structure that can be adjusted for different projects. It can be used as an empty box for branded packaging, seasonal gift programs, souvenir packaging, handmade product presentation, or retail-ready product sets. The design is simple enough for broad market use while still leaving room for custom branding.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"98zt1\" data-start=\"2898\" data-end=\"2929\">Material and Finish Options<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2930\" data-end=\"3261\">This product can be produced in different materials based on your target market and budget. Natural wood finishes, dark stained finishes, and unfinished wood box versions are available. If your project needs a more raw and natural look, an unfinished wood box with lid can also be supplied for craft or further decorating programs.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"c1e5i4\" data-start=\"3263\" data-end=\"3299\">OEM Size Logo and Insert Support<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3300\" data-end=\"3629\">As a B2B manufacturer, we support custom size, custom depth, logo engraving, UV printing, and custom inner structure. The box can be made with an empty inside space or with inserts such as EVA, paper card, foam, or velvet lining based on your product needs. This helps buyers use one box structure across different product lines.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"166xs6i\" data-start=\"3631\" data-end=\"3667\">Buyer Custom Packaging Available<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3668\" data-end=\"3958\">This page is for wholesale and custom production, not retail stock packing. Outer carton, barcode label, protective packing, insert setup, and shipping mark can be adjusted based on your order requirements. Buyer custom packaging is supported for export projects and private label programs.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"vxyi1c\" data-start=\"3960\" data-end=\"4005\">Good Fit for Wholesale and Brand Programs<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4006\" data-end=\"4326\">If you are looking for a small wooden box with lid that combines simple structure, easy customization, and broad application, this style is a practical option. It is especially suitable for custom gift packaging, wooden craft box programs, and branded wooden present boxes developed for medium and large quantity orders.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4328\" data-end=\"4331\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"1hryhf7\" data-start=\"4333\" data-end=\"4339\">FAQ<\/h2>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"sqm9bl\" data-start=\"4341\" data-end=\"4408\">1. Can you customize the size of this small wooden box with lid<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4409\" data-end=\"4636\">Yes. We do custom production for B2B buyers, so size adjustment is one of the most common requests. If you already have your product dimensions, we can suggest the right inner size and box proportion for your packaging project.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"nwawxx\" data-start=\"4638\" data-end=\"4711\">2. Is this more suitable for gift packaging or for wooden craft boxes<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4712\" data-end=\"4979\">Actually it works for both. Some customers use it as a clean wooden present box for branded gift sets, while others choose it as one of their wooden craft boxes for unfinished or semi-finished projects. The final use depends on the finish, insert, and logo treatment.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"f5des9\" data-start=\"4981\" data-end=\"5029\">3. Can you make it as an unfinished wood box<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"5030\" data-end=\"5278\">Yes, we can. If your market prefers a natural DIY look, we can supply an unfinished wood box with lid. This option is often used for craft projects, painting programs, laser branding, or customers who want to do their own surface treatment locally.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"we8plj\" data-start=\"5280\" data-end=\"5317\">4. What kind of logo can be added<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"5318\" data-end=\"5546\">The most common option is laser engraving, especially for buyers who want a clean and durable logo on a small wooden box with lid. Depending on the artwork and finish, UV printing or other branding methods can also be discussed.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"1vol1zs\" data-start=\"5548\" data-end=\"5611\">5. What products usually go inside this wooden box with lid<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"5612\" data-end=\"5832\">This type of box is usually used for jewelry, tea items, small accessories, cards, keepsakes, and promotional items. Some buyers also develop it into wooden present boxes for seasonal collections or brand gift packaging.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"13y7whp\" data-start=\"5834\" data-end=\"5872\">6. Do you provide retail packaging<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"5873\" data-end=\"6121\">We mainly support OEM and wholesale orders, so packaging is based on the buyer&#8217;s requirement rather than a fixed retail standard. If you need label packing, insert packing, gift sleeve, or export carton setup, we can work according to your project.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"hkbcj7\" data-start=\"6123\" data-end=\"6184\">7. Is this product suitable for wholesalers and importers<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"6185\" data-end=\"6428\">Yes, that is exactly the target customer. This page is written for wholesale buyers, importers, distributors, and brand owners looking for a stable manufacturer for custom small wooden box with lid projects, not for single-piece retail orders.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6185\" data-end=\"6428\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-6007\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Wooden-Storage-Box-9.jpg\" alt=\"wooden box with lid\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Wooden-Storage-Box-9.jpg 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Wooden-Storage-Box-9-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Wooden-Storage-Box-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Wooden-Storage-Box-9-768x768.jpg 76