ium Custom Walnut Wooden Ring Box for Jewelry Brands<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1800\">This custom wooden ring box is manufactured from solid walnut wood, designed for jewelry brands and wedding suppliers seeking premium packaging solutions. The heart shaped split opening structure creates emotional value while maintaining a compact and stable construction.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1857\">Why Choose Wooden Ring Box Instead of Paper Packaging<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1859\" data-end=\"2072\">Compared with paper ring boxes or plastic boxes, walnut wooden ring boxes significantly increase perceived product value. Luxury jewelry brands use wooden packaging to enhance retail pricing and brand positioning.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2074\" data-end=\"2105\">Factory Direct OEM Production<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2107\" data-end=\"2311\">We are a professional wooden jewelry packaging manufacturer in China, focusing on OEM bulk production. We support custom size, custom logo engraving, insert color customization and outer packaging design.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2313\" data-end=\"2353\">Stable Mass Production Quality Control<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2355\" data-end=\"2554\">Each wooden ring box undergoes moisture control, sanding, polishing and quality inspection before shipment. Color consistency and split alignment are strictly controlled to reduce bulk order defects.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2556\" data-end=\"2596\">Heart Shaped Design for Wedding Market<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2598\" data-end=\"2786\">The heart shaped wooden ring box is especially suitable for engagement proposal and wedding ceremony projects. It adds emotional presentation value for bridal brands and boutique jewelers.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2788\" data-end=\"2823\">Lightweight Yet Durable Structure<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2825\" data-end=\"2962\">Despite using solid walnut, the structure is compact and lightweight, making it suitable for international export and wholesale shipping.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2964\" data-end=\"2997\">Eco Friendly Reusable Packaging<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2999\" data-end=\"3169\">Wooden ring box offers reusable and sustainable packaging compared with disposable cardboard boxes. It meets increasing eco packaging demands in Europe and North America.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3171\" data-end=\"3187\">Target Clients<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3189\" data-end=\"3343\">Suitable for wedding jewelry brands, boutique jewelers, gift packaging distributors and private label importers looking for long term factory cooperation.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3391\" data-end=\"3407\">\n<p data-start=\"3409\" data-end=\"3640\">Q1 Can I put my logo on the wooden ring box<br data-start=\"3452\" data-end=\"3455\" \/>Yes. We support laser engraving, UV printing and silk printing. Most clients prefer subtle laser engraving for premium positioning. Sample proof will be provided before mass production.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3642\" data-end=\"3829\">Q2 What is your minimum order quantity<br data-start=\"3680\" data-end=\"3683\" \/>Our standard MOQ is 100 pieces per design. For customized shape or structure adjustments, MOQ may vary slightly depending on tooling requirements.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3831\" data-end=\"4067\">Q3 How do you ensure color consistency for walnut wood<br data-start=\"3885\" data-end=\"3888\" \/>We control wood sourcing batches and conduct pre production color selection. Slight natural wood variation is normal, but we maintain consistent tone within each production batch.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4069\" data-end=\"4290\">Q4 Can you provide custom outer packaging<br data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4113\" \/>Yes. We can produce custom paper outer boxes, gift sleeves and export cartons according to your brand packaging system. Wooden box and outer packaging can be developed together.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4292\" data-end=\"4486\">Q5 How long does production take for bulk orders<br data-start=\"4340\" data-end=\"4343\" \/>Normal production lead time is 20 to 30 days after sample confirmation. For urgent wedding season projects, we can discuss priority scheduling.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1205\">Product Name<br data-start=\"1173\" data-end=\"1176\" \/>Custom Walnut Wooden Ring Box<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1207\" data-end=\"1235\">Material<br data-start=\"1215\" data-end=\"1218\" \/>Solid Walnut Wood<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1237\" data-end=\"1270\">Shape<br data-start=\"1242\" data-end=\"1245\" \/>Heart Shaped Split Design<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1272\" data-end=\"1297\">Insert<br data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1281\" \/>Velvet Ring Slot<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1338\">Logo<br data-start=\"1303\" data-end=\"1306\" \/>Laser Engraving Custom Available<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1340\" data-end=\"1356\">MOQ<br data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1346\" \/>100 Pieces<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1358\" data-end=\"1389\">Production Time<br data-start=\"1373\" data-end=\"1376\" \/>20 to 30 Days<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1391\" data-end=\"1456\">Application<br data-start=\"1402\" data-end=\"1405\" \/>Wedding Ring Packaging Engagement Jewelry Packaging<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5955,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[108],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-5951","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-wooden-jewelry-boxes","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"shipping-taxable","11":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/5951","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5951"}],"wp:featuredmedia"