-end=\"1654\" \/>Raw wood is graded before production.<br data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1694\" \/>Hardware is sourced from stable long-term suppliers.<br data-start=\"1746\" data-end=\"1749\" \/>Insert materials such as EVA, velvet, PU leather or paperboard are customized based on your brand positioning.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1861\" data-end=\"2022\">Quality Control<br data-start=\"1876\" data-end=\"1879\" \/>Pre-production sample approval<br data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1912\" \/>In-line QC during sanding and spraying<br data-start=\"1950\" data-end=\"1953\" \/>Final inspection before packing<br data-start=\"1984\" data-end=\"1987\" \/>Drop-test standard export packaging<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2024\" data-end=\"2158\">FBA &amp; Export Support<br data-start=\"2044\" data-end=\"2047\" \/>Barcode labeling<br data-start=\"2063\" data-end=\"2066\" \/>Drop test packaging<br data-start=\"2085\" data-end=\"2088\" \/>Reinforced master cartons<br data-start=\"2113\" data-end=\"2116\" \/>FSC material optional<br data-start=\"2137\" data-end=\"2140\" \/>HS code assistance<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2160\" data-end=\"2301\">We mainly supply:<br data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2180\" \/>Jewelry brands<br data-start=\"2194\" data-end=\"2197\" \/>Watch brands<br data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2212\" \/>Display packaging distributors<br data-start=\"2242\" data-end=\"2245\" \/>Gift packaging wholesalers<br data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2274\" \/>Private label bulk buyers<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2303\" data-end=\"2323\">\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2325\" data-end=\"2344\">FAQ<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2346\" data-end=\"2571\">Q1: What if the glass breaks during shipping?<br data-start=\"2391\" data-end=\"2394\" \/>We apply protective film on glass, foam protection inside and 5-layer export cartons. Drop tests are conducted before shipment. Replacement support is available for bulk orders.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2573\" data-end=\"2708\">Q2: Can you support small MOQ?<br data-start=\"2603\" data-end=\"2606\" \/>For standard sizes, MOQ can start from around 300 pcs. Custom structural molds may require higher MOQ.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2710\" data-end=\"2883\">Q3: How do you prevent wood cracking?<br data-start=\"2747\" data-end=\"2750\" \/>We strictly control moisture level and allow wood conditioning before production. Structural stress areas near hinges are reinforced.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2885\" data-end=\"3026\">Q4: Can you match our brand color?<br data-start=\"2919\" data-end=\"2922\" \/>Yes. We provide color samples before bulk production and confirm under standardized lighting conditions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3028\" data-end=\"3136\">Q5: Can we mix multiple models in one container?<br data-start=\"3076\" data-end=\"3079\" \/>Yes. We support mixed SKUs to help optimize freight cost.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p data-start=\"737\" data-end=\"787\">Material<br data-start=\"745\" data-end=\"748\" \/>Solid Pine \/ Acacia \/ Walnut optional<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"789\" data-end=\"835\">Size<br data-start=\"793\" data-end=\"796\" \/>Fully customized dimensions available<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"922\">OEM \/ ODM<br data-start=\"846\" data-end=\"849\" \/>Logo engraving, UV printing, hot stamping, custom velvet or EVA inserts<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"983\">Lead Time<br data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"936\" \/>Sample 7\u201310 days<br data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"955\" \/>Bulk production 25\u201335 days<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"985\" data-end=\"1036\">MOQ<br data-start=\"988\" data-end=\"991\" \/>Normally 300\u2013500 pcs depending on structure<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1038\" data-end=\"1101\">Structure<br data-start=\"1047\" data-end=\"1050\" \/>Glass lid + metal lock + reinforced corner joints<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5950,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template