ode=\"16\">wooden watch box wholesale<\/h2>\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"16\">Elevate Your Brand with Our Luxury Wooden Watch Box Wholesale Collection<\/h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\">When it comes to high-end watch packaging, presentation is everything. As a leading <b data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"84\">custom watch display case supplier<\/b>, we designed this classic high-gloss wooden watch box to help retailers and watch brands increase their product&#8217;s perceived value and boost profit margins.<\/p>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"18\">Craftsmanship That Speaks for Itself<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\">Unlike cheap MDF alternatives, this watch display case is built for longevity and elegance.<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"20\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Elegant Finish:<\/b> The exterior boasts a multi-layer high-gloss piano lacquer finish, giving it a rich, sophisticated mahogany\/cherry wood appearance.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Clear Display:<\/b> A scratch-resistant glass top allows collectors to view their timepieces while protecting them from dust and moisture.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Premium Hardware:<\/b> Upgraded gold-tone metal hinges and a secure lock add a touch of vintage luxury while ensuring the lid stays firmly open or safely closed.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Plush Interior:<\/b> Soft, removable velvet pillows securely hold watches of all sizes (from delicate women&#8217;s watches to heavy men&#8217;s chronographs) without scratching the bands.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"21\">Flexible Customization for B2B Clients<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">We understand that your packaging is an extension of your brand. We offer comprehensive OEM\/ODM services:<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"23\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Logo Application:<\/b> Add your brand logo via silk-screening, hot stamping, or a custom 3D metal plate on the glass or the wood.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Capacity Variations:<\/b> Mix and match different slot sizes (e.g., 5-slot, 10-slot, 12-slot, or dual-layer 20-slot) within your bulk order.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Packaging:<\/b> Custom color boxes, protective sleeves, and barcode labeling available for direct-to-retail readiness.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"24\">Why Partner with Us?<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\">Sourcing <b data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"9\">bulk luxury watch boxes<\/b> shouldn&#8217;t be a headache. We offer <b data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"67\">low MOQ<\/b> options for new business partners testing the market, backed by a 100% quality inspection process before shipping. Whether you need 100 pieces for a corporate event or 5,000 pieces for your retail chain, we guarantee stable lead times and competitive factory pricing.<\/p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"26\" \/>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: What is the minimum order quantity (MOQ) for this watch box?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"64\">A:<\/b> If you just need the blank boxes without any logo, our MOQ is very flexible\u2014usually starting at just 50 pieces. If you need custom logos or custom packaging, the MOQ is 100 to 200 pieces, depending on the specific customization method. Just shoot us a message with what you have in mind!<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I mix different sizes (like 6-slot and 12-slot) in one wholesale order?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"79\">A:<\/b> Absolutely. We know retailers need variety. You can mix different capacities in a single order to meet the MOQ, as long as we have the base models in stock.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><b data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: How do you put my brand logo on the box?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><b data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">A:<\/b> The most popular options for this high-gloss finish are gold\/silver foil stamping on the inside lid, silk-screen printing on the glass, or applying a custom metal nameplate on the front. Send us your logo file (AI or PDF), and we\u2019ll make a digital mockup for you for free.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: What\u2019s the lead time for a bulk order?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"42\">A:<\/b> For standard non-customized stock, we can ship within 5-7 days. For custom orders (with your logo), it usually takes about 15-25 days for production. We always recommend confirming the schedule with us if you have a tight deadline for a product launch or holiday season.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Are the pillows inside large enough for heavy men&#8217;s watches?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"64\">A:<\/b> Yes. We designed the grid width and the pillows to comfortably fit modern oversized watches (up to 50mm case size) without them touching each other. The pillows are also squishy enough to accommodate smaller women&#8217;s bands.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p da