s chocolate protected while maintaining display aesthetics.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2185\" data-end=\"2188\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2190\" data-end=\"2214\">Customization Options<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2250\">We support full OEM customization:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2252\" data-end=\"2270\">Window Options<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2325\">\n<li data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2286\">\n<p data-start=\"2273\" data-end=\"2286\">Clear acrylic<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2287\" data-end=\"2304\">\n<p data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2304\">Frosted acrylic<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2305\" data-end=\"2325\">\n<p data-start=\"2307\" data-end=\"2325\">Custom window size<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2327\" data-end=\"2346\">Internal Layout<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2430\">\n<li data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2369\">\n<p data-start=\"2349\" data-end=\"2369\">6 grid chocolate box<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2370\" data-end=\"2385\">\n<p data-start=\"2372\" data-end=\"2385\">9 grid layout<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2386\" data-end=\"2411\">\n<p data-start=\"2388\" data-end=\"2411\">Custom compartment size<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2412\" data-end=\"2430\">\n<p data-start=\"2414\" data-end=\"2430\">Removable insert<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2432\" data-end=\"2444\">Branding<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2445\" data-end=\"2496\">\n<li data-start=\"2445\" data-end=\"2462\">\n<p data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2462\">Laser engraving<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2463\" data-end=\"2481\">\n<p data-start=\"2465\" data-end=\"2481\">UV logo printing<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2482\" data-end=\"2496\">\n<p data-start=\"2484\" data-end=\"2496\">Hot stamping<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2498\" data-end=\"2501\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2530\">Designed for Bulk Orders<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2532\" data-end=\"2599\">As a wooden box manufacturer in China, we focus on B2B cooperation:<