itional hardware. We test sliding smoothness before shipment.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3255\" data-end=\"3258\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3260\" data-end=\"3306\">2. Will the acrylic window scratch easily?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3308\" data-end=\"3437\">We use protective film during production and shipping. For retail display, acrylic provides clear visibility and good durability.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3439\" data-end=\"3442\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3444\" data-end=\"3499\">3. Is this box suitable for international shipping?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3584\">Yes. The simple sliding structure reduces hardware-related damage during transport.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3586\" data-end=\"3589\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3591\" data-end=\"3630\">4. Can I customize the window size?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3632\" data-end=\"3704\">Yes. Window shape and size can be adjusted based on your product layout.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3706\" data-end=\"3709\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3711\" data-end=\"3775\">5. What makes this different from your drawer chocolate box?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3777\" data-end=\"3942\">Drawer structure slides out from the front, while sliding lid structure moves horizontally on top. Sliding lid version offers visible display through acrylic window.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We manufacture sliding lid wooden chocolate boxes with acrylic window for chocolate brands and wholesale buyers. Precision sliding rail structure, clean hardware-free design, visible product display, OEM customization available.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5914,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[66],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-5913","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-wooden-gift-box","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"shipping-taxable","11":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{