>\n<h3 data-start=\"2967\" data-end=\"3019\">1. Is the drawer smooth enough for repeated use?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3021\" data-end=\"3155\">Yes. We control sliding tolerance during production to ensure smooth movement. It does not require metal rails or additional hardware.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3157\" data-end=\"3160\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3162\" data-end=\"3208\">2. Will the drawer become loose over time?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3210\" data-end=\"3316\">Under normal retail use, it remains stable. For bulk export, we test structural tightness before shipment.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3318\" data-end=\"3321\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3323\" data-end=\"3364\">3. Can the drawer size be customized?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3366\" data-end=\"3468\">Yes. You can provide your chocolate dimensions, and we adjust internal grid and box depth accordingly.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3470\" data-end=\"3473\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3475\" data-end=\"3520\">4. Is pine wood strong enough for export?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3522\" data-end=\"3638\">Yes. Pine is widely used in wooden packaging for export markets. It offers a good balance between strength and cost.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3640\" data-end=\"3643\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3645\" data-end=\"3707\">5. How is this different from your magnetic chocolate box?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3709\" data-end=\"3845\">This version focuses on a hardware-free slide structure. It provides a cleaner design and avoids magnet alignment or hinge installation.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We manufacture pine drawer wooden chocolate boxes with slide-out structure for chocolate brands and wholesale buyers. Clean design, no magnets, customizable grid layout, bulk production ready.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5912,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[66],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-5906","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish