ta-end=\"1982\">Suitable for corporate gifts<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1983\" data-end=\"2008\">\n<p data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2008\">Strong shelf presence<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2033\">Natural Wood Finish<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2125\">\n<li data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2062\">\n<p data-start=\"2036\" data-end=\"2062\">Lightweight modern style<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2063\" data-end=\"2094\">\n<p data-start=\"2065\" data-end=\"2094\">Suitable for younger brands<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2095\" data-end=\"2125\">\n<p data-start=\"2097\" data-end=\"2125\">Cost-efficient positioning<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2127\" data-end=\"2202\">Different finish, same magnetic structure \u2014 flexible for brand positioning.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2204\" data-end=\"2207\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2246\">Built for Wholesale &amp; Brand Owners<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2248\" data-end=\"2326\">As a direct OEM wooden box manufacturer in China, we focus on bulk production:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2328\" data-end=\"2464\">\u2714 MOQ from 300\u2013500 pcs<br data-start=\"2350\" data-end=\"2353\" \/>\u2714 Stable magnetic alignment<br data-start=\"2380\" data-end=\"2383\" \/>\u2714 Controlled wood moisture<br data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2412\" \/>\u2714 Custom logo engraving<br data-start=\"2435\" data-end=\"2438\" \/>\u2714 Flexible insert layout<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2466\" data-end=\"2479\">We work with:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2596\">\n<li data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2507\">\n<p data-start=\"2483\" data-end=\"2507\">Chocolate brand owners<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2539\">\n<p data-start=\"2510\" data-end=\"2539\">Gift packaging distributors<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2540\" data-end=\"2568\">\n<p data-start=\"2542\" data-end=\"2568\">Corporate gift suppliers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2569\" data-end=\"2596\">\n<p data-start=\"2571\" 