655\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1703\">Why Paulownia Wood for Chocolate Packaging?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1705\" data-end=\"1769\">Paulownia wood is widely used in export packaging because it is:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1771\" data-end=\"1893\">\u2022 Lightweight<br data-start=\"1784\" data-end=\"1787\" \/>\u2022 Stable in dry conditions<br data-start=\"1813\" data-end=\"1816\" \/>\u2022 Cost-effective<br data-start=\"1832\" data-end=\"1835\" \/>\u2022 Easy to laser engrave<br data-start=\"1858\" data-end=\"1861\" \/>\u2022 Suitable for bulk production<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1985\">For distributors importing large quantities, this significantly reduces shipping expenses.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1987\" data-end=\"1990\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2017\">Available Grid Options<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2019\" data-end=\"2054\">We offer flexible internal layouts:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2179\">\n<li data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2094\">\n<p data-start=\"2058\" data-end=\"2094\">6 compartment wooden chocolate box<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2095\" data-end=\"2124\">\n<p data-start=\"2097\" data-end=\"2124\">9 grid chocolate gift box<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2125\" data-end=\"2154\">\n<p data-start=\"2127\" data-end=\"2154\">Custom removable dividers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2179\">\n<p data-start=\"2157\" data-end=\"2179\">EVA + velvet inserts<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2181\" data-end=\"2238\">Grid layout can be adjusted based on your chocolate size.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2240\" data-end=\"2243\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2245\" data-end=\"2270\">Magnetic Lid Structure<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2272\" data-end=\"2317\">The box comes with a magnetic closure system:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2444\">\u2714 Smooth opening and closing<br data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2350\" \/>\u2714 Hidden magnet option<br data-start=\"2372\" data-end=\"2375\" \/>\u2714 Secure alignment during transport<br data-start=\"2410\" data-end=\"2413\" \/>\u2714 Premium retail presentation<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2446\" data-end=\"2449\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2451\" data-end=\"2479\">OEM Customization Options<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2515\">As a factory supplier, we support:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2517\" data-end=\"2639\">\n<li data-start=\"2517\" data-end=\"2536\">\n<p data-start=\"2519\" data-end=\"2536\">Custom box size<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2562\">\n<p data-start=\"2539\" data-end=\"2562\">Custom logo engraving<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2563\" data-end=\"2582\">\n<p data-start=\"2565\" data-end=\"2582\">Color finishing<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2611\">\n<p data-start=\"2585\" data-end=\"2611\">Inner tray customization<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2612\" data-end=\"2639\">\n<p data-start=\"2614\" data-end=\"2639\">Private label packaging<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2641\" data-end=\"2691\">We focus on bulk orders and wholesale cooperation.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2696\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2698\" data-end=\"2713\">Ideal Buyers<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2715\" data-end=\"2767\">This paulownia wooden chocolate box is suitable for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2769\" data-end=\"2912\">\n<li data-start=\"2769\" data-end=\"2794\">\n<p data-start=\"2771\" data-end=\"2794\">Chocolate wholesalers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2795\" data-end=\"2825\">\n<p data-start=\"2797\" data-end=\"2825\">Seasonal gift distributors<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2826\" data-end=\"2853\">\n<p data-start=\"2828\" data-end=\"2853\">E-commerce brand owners<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2854\" data-end=\"2881\">\n<p data-start=\"2856\" data-end=\"2881\">Private label importers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2882\" data-end=\"2912\">\n<p data-start=\"2884\" data-end=\"2912\">Promotional gift companies<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2914\" data-end=\"2917\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2919\" data-end=\"2943\">Bulk Production &amp; MOQ<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2945\" data-end=\"3077\">\u2022 MOQ starting from 300\u2013500 pcs<br data-start=\"2976\" data-end=\"2979\" \/>\u2022 Sample available before mass production<br data-start=\"3020\" data-end=\"3023\" \/>\u2022 Stable moisture control<br data-start=\"3048\" data-end=\"3051\" \/>\u2022 Export-ready packaging<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3079\" data-end=\"3151\">For high-volume orders, paulownia wood helps optimize total landed cost.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3153\" data-end=\"3156\" \/>\n<h1 data-start=\"3158\" data-end=\"3173\">FAQ<\/h1>\n<h3 data-start=\"3175\" data-end=\"3228\">1. Why choose paulownia instead of walnut or oak?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3230\" data-end=\"3404\">Paulownia is much lighter and more cost-efficient. If your focus is bulk export and competitive pricing, it is a practical option while still maintaining a clean wooden look.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3406\" data-end=\"3409\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3411\" data-end=\"3455\">2. Will the box feel too light or cheap?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3457\" data-end=\"3618\">Not at all. With proper finishing and magnetic closure, it still looks premium. The weight is reduced mainly to lower shipping cost, not to compromise structure.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3620\" data-end=\"3623\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3625\" data-end=\"3680\">3. Can I use this box for premium chocolate brands?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3682\" data-end=\"3872\">Yes. Many growing chocolate brands use paulownia packaging to balance cost and brand image. For ultra-luxury positioning, hardwood may be preferred, but for scale, paulownia works very well.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3874\" data-end=\"3877\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3879\" data-end=\"3935\">4. Can the grid be changed to fit my chocolate size?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3937\" data-end=\"4031\">Yes. You can send your chocolate dimensions, and we will adjust insert or divider accordingly.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4033\" data-end=\"4036\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4089\">5. Is this suitable for international shipping?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4091\" data-end=\"4224\">Yes. Paulownia is commonly used in export packaging due to its lightweight structure. We also ensure proper drying before production.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We supply lightweight paulownia wooden chocolate boxes designed for bulk export and cost-efficient luxury packaging. Ideal for chocolate brands, gift wholesalers, and distributors seeking lower shipping cost with premium presentation.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5898,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[66],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-5893","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-wooden-gift-box","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"shipping-taxable","11":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/5893","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5893"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5898"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5893"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=5893"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=5893"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=5893"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}},{"id":5886,"date":"2026-02-11T14:00:43","date_gmt":"2026-02-11T14:00:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=5886"},"modified":"2026-02-11T14:00:44","modified_gmt":"2026-02-11T14:00:44","slug":"magnetic-wooden-chocolate-box-manufacturer","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/product\/magnetic-wooden-chocolate-box-manufacturer\/","title":{"rendered":"Custom Magnetic Wooden Chocolate Box Manufacturer | OEM Luxury Chocolate Packaging Supplier"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1 data-start=\"1192\" data-end=\"1263\">Source from magnetic wooden chocolate box manufacturer<\/h1>\n<h2 data-start=\"1192\" data-end=\"1263\">Custom Magnetic Wooden Chocolate Box for Premium Chocolate Packaging<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1516\">If you are sourcing high-end chocolate packaging, a magnetic wooden chocolate box offers both durability and luxury presentation. Compared with paper or plastic packaging, wooden chocolate boxes elevate brand value and increase perceived retail price.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1518\" data-end=\"1621\">As a direct wooden box manufacturer in China, we specialize in OEM magnetic wooden chocolate boxes for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1623\" data-end=\"1734\">\n<li data-start=\"1623\" data-end=\"1643\">\n<p data-start=\"1625\" data-end=\"1643\">Chocolate brands<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1644\" data-end=\"1674\">\n<p data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1674\">Gift packaging wholesalers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1675\" data-end=\"1705\">\n<p data-start=\"1677\" data-end=\"1705\">Private label distributors<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1706\" data-end=\"1734\">\n<p data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1734\">Corporate gift suppliers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1736\" data-end=\"1739\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1741\" data-end=\"1792\">Why Magnetic Wooden Chocolate Boxes Are Trending<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1794\" data-end=\"1941\">Luxury chocolate packaging is no longer disposable. Many premium brands now choose reusable wooden chocolate boxes with magnetic lids because they:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"2098\">\u2022 Improve brand positioning<br data-start=\"1970\" data-end=\"1973\" \/>\u2022 Increase gift value<br data-start=\"1994\" data-end=\"1997\" \/>\u2022 Support logo engraving<br data-start=\"2021\" data-end=\"2024\" \/>\u2022 Allow custom insert layout<br data-start=\"2052\" data-end=\"2055\" \/>\u2022 Reduce packaging damage during shipping<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2188\">Magnetic closure adds a smooth, high-end user experience compared to traditional hinges.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2190\" data-end=\"2193\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2195\" data-end=\"2239\">Customization Options (OEM\/ODM Available)<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2303\">We support full customization based on your brand positioning:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2305\" data-end=\"2333\">1. Wood Material Options<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2334\" data-end=\"2439\">\n<li data-start=\"2334\" data-end=\"2361\">\n<p data-start=\"2336\" data-end=\"2361\">Pine wood (budget series)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2362\" data-end=\"2407\">\n<p data-start=\"2364\" data-end=\"2407\">Rubber wood \/ Acacia wood (standard series)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2408\" data-end=\"2439\">\n<p data-start=\"2410\" data-end=\"2439\">Walnut \/ Oak (premium series)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2441\" data-end=\"2470\">2. Magnetic Lid Structure<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2471\" data-end=\"2538\">\n<li data-start=\"2471\" data-end=\"2487\">\n<p data-start=\"2473\" data-end=\"2487\">Hidden magnets<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2505\">\n<p data-start=\"2490\" data-end=\"2505\">Visible magnets<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2506\" data-end=\"2538\">\n<p data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2538\">Single or double magnet design<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2540\" data-end=\"2563\">3. Insert Solutions<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2564\" data-end=\"2654\">\n<li data-start=\"2564\" data-end=\"2586\">\n<p data-start=\"2566\" data-end=\"2586\">EVA foam with velvet<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2587\" data-end=\"2616\">\n<p data-start=\"2589\" data-end=\"2616\">Food-grade cardboard insert<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2617\" data-end=\"2634\">\n<p data-start=\"2619\" data-end=\"2634\">Paper pulp tray<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2635\" data-end=\"2654\">\n<p data-start=\"2637\" data-end=\"2654\">Removable divider<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2656\" data-end=\"2675\">4. Logo Options<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2676\" data-end=\"2740\">\n<li data-start=\"2676\" data-end=\"2693\">\n<p data-start=\"2678\" data-end=\"2693\">Laser engraving<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2694\" data-end=\"2707\">\n<p data-start=\"2696\" data-end=\"2707\">UV printing<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2708\" data-end=\"2722\">\n<p data-start=\"2710\" data-end=\"2722\">Hot stamping<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2723\" data-end=\"2740\">\n<p data-start=\"2725\" data-end=\"2740\">Metal nameplate<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2742\" data-end=\"2745\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2747\" data-end=\"2783\">Built for Wholesale &amp; Bulk Orders<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2785\" data-end=\"2835\">Unlike retail sellers, we focus on B2B production.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2837\" data-end=\"2982\">\u2714 MOQ starting from 300\u2013500 pcs<br data-start=\"2868\" data-end=\"2871\" \/>\u2714 Stable mass production<br data-start=\"2895\" data-end=\"2898\" \/>\u2714 Moisture control 6\u201312%<br data-start=\"2922\" data-end=\"2925\" \/>\u2714 Export-compliant packaging<br data-start=\"2953\" data-end=\"2956\" \/>\u2714 Factory direct pricing<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2984\" data-end=\"3106\">We understand that for chocolate brands, packaging cost, consistency, and delivery time matter more than decoration alone.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3108\" data-end=\"3111\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"3113\" data-end=\"3125\">Ideal For<\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"3127\" data-end=\"3299\">\n<li data-start=\"3127\" data-end=\"3159\">\n<p data-start=\"3129\" data-end=\"3159\">Premium chocolate gift boxes<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3160\" data-end=\"3195\">\n<p data-start=\"3162\" data-end=\"3195\">Christmas chocolate collections<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3196\" data-end=\"3230\">\n<p data-start=\"3198\" data-end=\"3230\">Valentine\u2019s Day gift packaging<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3231\" data-end=\"3260\">\n<p data-start=\"3233\" data-end=\"3260\">Corporate chocolate gifts<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3261\" data-end=\"3299\">\n<p data-start=\"3263\" data-end=\"3299\">Limited edition chocolate launches<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"3301\" data-end=\"3304\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"3306\" data-end=\"3373\">Why Work With a Wooden Box Factory Instead of a Trading Company?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3375\" data-end=\"3401\">As a factory manufacturer:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3403\" data-end=\"3559\">\u2022 We control moisture level and wood quality<br data-start=\"3447\" data-end=\"3450\" \/>\u2022 We ensure magnetic alignment accuracy<br data-start=\"3489\" data-end=\"3492\" \/>\u2022 We manage bulk tolerance control<br data-start=\"3526\" data-end=\"3529\" \/>\u2022 We reduce middleman markup<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3561\" data-end=\"3643\">For wholesalers and brand owners, this means stable pricing and reliable delivery.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3675\" data-end=\"3751\">1. What is your minimum order quantity for custom chocolate wooden boxes?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3753\" data-end=\"3974\">For most standard sizes, our MOQ starts from 300 to 500 pieces depending on structure and finishing. If you need a completely new mold or special insert layout, MOQ may vary slightly. We can discuss based on your project.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3976\" data-end=\"3979\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"3981\" data-end=\"4029\">2. Can the wooden chocolate box be food safe?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4031\" data-end=\"4244\">The chocolate does not directly touch the wood. Normally, we provide food-grade paper tray, cardboard insert, or EVA with food-safe wrapping. If required, we can adjust finishing to meet specific market standards.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4246\" data-end=\"4249\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"4251\" data-end=\"4312\">3. How strong are the magnets? Will they loosen over time?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4314\" data-end=\"4520\">We use embedded strong magnets. They are fixed inside the lid structure and will not fall out under normal use. For export orders, we test magnetic alignment during mass production to ensure smooth closing.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4522\" data-end=\"4525\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"4527\" data-end=\"4599\">4. Can I customize the internal layout for different chocolate sizes?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4601\" data-end=\"4767\">Yes. You can provide your chocolate size or tray dimensions, and we can design insert layout accordingly. Removable inserts are also possible if you need flexibility.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4769\" data-end=\"4772\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"4845\">5. What wood material do you recommend for premium chocolate brands?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4847\" data-end=\"5015\">For luxury positioning, walnut or oak works best visually. For cost-sensitive markets, rubber wood or pine is more budget-friendly while still maintaining a clean look.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"5017\" data-end=\"5020\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"5022\" data-end=\"5074\">6. Do you provide samples before mass production?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"5076\" data-end=\"5199\">Yes, we strongly recommend sampling for new projects. Sample time usually takes 7\u201312 days depending on customization level.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We manufacture custom magnetic wooden chocolate boxes for premium chocolate brands, distributors, and gift packaging wholesalers. Designed for luxury retail presentation, our wooden chocolate packaging supports custom logo, size, ins