le | Custom Logo Factory Supplier for Restaurants &#038; FBA Sellers"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1 data-path-to-node=\"14\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wholesale Wooden Utensil Holder<\/b><\/h1>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Stop dealing with flimsy plastic organizers that break in a month.<\/b> We\u2019ve been in the woodware industry in Xiamen long enough to know that for restaurants and catering, durability is everything. That\u2019s why we use high-density solid wood and a reinforced metal handle. This caddy doesn&#8217;t just look good on a table; it&#8217;s built to survive the rush hour of a busy bistro. When your customers feel the weight of this holder, they know they\u2019re getting quality\u2014and that means zero returns for you.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><b data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Your Brand, Our Craftsmanship.<\/b> We understand that branding is how you win in a crowded market. Whether you\u2019re an Amazon seller or a hotel supplier, we offer precision laser engraving that makes your logo pop. We handle the &#8220;dirty work&#8221; of production and QC so you can focus on scaling. Our facility is optimized for bulk runs, but we keep our MOQs flexible because we know today&#8217;s small test order is tomorrow&#8217;s full container.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">FBA Ready? We\u2019re Way Ahead of You.<\/b> Shipping damage is a profit killer. We\u2019ve already done the homework\u2014our packaging is drop-test approved and designed to meet strict FBA warehouse requirements. We provide individual labeling and reinforced master cartons so you can ship directly from our factory to the Amazon warehouse without touching a single box. 15-day dispatch is our promise, keeping your inventory healthy and your &#8220;Out of Stock&#8221; alerts away.<\/p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"17\" \/>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"18\">FAQ (The Real Talk)<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;I want to test the market first. What\u2019s your real MOQ for custom logos?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">A:<\/b> Look, we love supporting growing brands. We\u2019ve kept the MOQ for laser logos very accessible. Send me your vector file, and I\u2019ll have a digital mockup ready for you within 24 hours. Let&#8217;s start small and grow together.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;How can I be sure the metal handle won&#8217;t rust or come loose?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"66\">A:<\/b> We use a powder-coated finish on the iron handles to prevent rust, even in humid restaurant environments. Every handle is bolted securely and tested for weight-bearing before it leaves our QC line. We build these to be workhorses, not just decorations.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;What\u2019s your policy if a shipment arrives with cracked wood?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"65\">A:<\/b> We pack these with 5-layer corrugated boxes and protective wrap. But if the shipping company is rough and something breaks, just snap a photo and send it to me. I\u2019ll replace it in your next batch or refund the difference immediately. I\u2019m here for a long-term partnership, not a quick win.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><b data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;Can you handle 5,000 units in a single run?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">A:<\/b> Yes. We have the production capacity to handle large-scale wholesale orders while maintaining our 15-day dispatch standard. If you have a massive project, let&#8217;s talk about a staggered shipping schedule to keep your cash flow optimiz