 you can see exactly how it looks before we start the machines.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;I&#8217;ve been burned by late deliveries. How&#8217;s your schedule?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"63\">A:<\/b> I\u2019ll be direct with you: if it\u2019s in stock, it\u2019s out the door in 7 days. For custom bulk runs, we usually need 15 to 20 days. I won&#8217;t give you a fake date just to get the deposit; if there&#8217;s a delay, you&#8217;ll hear it from me first.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;What if the shipment arrives and something is broken?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"59\">A:<\/b> We pack these things to survive a rough sea voyage, but stuff happens. If anything arrives damaged due to our packing, just snap a photo. I\u2019ll replace them in your next batch or credit your account immediately. We&#8217;re in this for the long term, not a one-time deal.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><b data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: &#8220;Is the wood finish really food-safe?&#8221;<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"42\">A:<\/b> Absolutely. It\u2019s 100% natural wood with a food-grade protective coating. If your market requires specific lab reports like LFGB or FDA for customs, let me know early so we can get the paperwork ready for you.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5739\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/wooden-salt-box-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/wooden-salt-box-10.jpg 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/wooden-salt-box-10-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20