 Wood Essential Oil Trays<\/b> are designed for retailers, spa owners, and Amazon sellers who want to add value to their product line. Made from durable, eco-friendly timber, these trays turn a messy collection into a professional display.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Heading 2: Why Source This Tray From Us?<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Versatile Fit:<\/b> Don&#8217;t worry about bottle sizes. Our stepped-hole design secures 5ml to 15ml bottles and even rollerballs without wobbling.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Retail-Ready Finish:<\/b> Smoothly sanded, burr-free, and coated with protective varnish. Ready for Amazon FBA or boutique shelves immediately.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Your Brand, Your Design:<\/b> We offer laser engraving for your logo. Building your own aromatherapy brand has never been easier.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Built for Safety:<\/b> The deep-slot design prevents expensive oils from tipping over and breaking during display or use.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><b data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Heading 3: Specifications<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Material:<\/b> High-grade Solid Wood (Sustainable source).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Hole Diameter:<\/b> 3cm (Standard) &#8211; Fits most doTERRA \/ Young Living \/ Plant Therapy bottles.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MOQ:<\/b> 50 pcs for standard stock; 200 pcs for custom logo.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Packaging:<\/b> Individual bubble wrap + sturdy carton box (Safe for export).<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">FAQ<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I mix different sizes in one order?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"43\">A:<\/b> Yes. We know you might want to test the market. You can mix the 6-hole and 12-hole trays in your first carton to see which one sells better.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><b data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Is the wood actually solid or just veneer?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"46\">A:<\/b> It\u2019s 100% solid wood. No particle board, no fake veneer. It\u2019s heavy, durable, and feels expensive in your hand. Your customers will tell the difference immediately.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><b data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: I sell on Amazon. Can you stick my barcode labels?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"54\">A:<\/b> Absolutely. We work with many Amazon sellers. Send us your FNSKU labels, and we will stick them on each box for free before shipping. We can also pack them in sets if you sell bundles.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: How much is the logo engraving?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"35\">A:<\/b> It depends on your quantity. For orders over 200 pieces, we often include simple logo engraving for free. Send me your AI\/PDF file, and let&#8217;s talk.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><b data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: What if the trays arrive cracked?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"37\">A:<\/b> We use double-layer protection, but shipping accidents happen. If you receive any broken units,<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\">show me the photos within 7 days, and I will replace them or refund you in the next order. No excuses.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,3,0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5663\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289-600x600.png 600w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180638_289-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5662\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180632_528.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180632_528.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180632_528-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180632_528-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ScreenShot_2026-02-04_180632_528-768x768.png 768w, https:\