erial Versatility:<\/b> Choose from premium <b data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"42\">Walnut, Oak, Pine, or Bamboo<\/b>. We use eco-friendly varnish that meets international export standards.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">E-Commerce Ready Packaging:<\/b> Tired of receiving broken wood products? We use reinforced EPE foam and sturdy inner boxes that pass rigorous drop tests, ensuring your goods arrive ready for retail or FBA shipment.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"24\"><b data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Specifications<\/b><\/h4>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"25\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Material:<\/b> 100% Natural Solid Wood<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dimensions:<\/b> [Insert your size, e.g., 15cm x 12cm x 18cm]<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Capacity:<\/b> Suitable for pets up to [Insert weight, e.g., 40 lbs] prior to cremation.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Finish:<\/b> Natural Wood Oil \/ Varnish \/ Vintage Stain<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"26\" \/>\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\">5. FAQ<\/h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I change the wood color to match my current product line?<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"65\">A:<\/b> Absolutely. We know consistency is key for your brand. Whether you need a dark walnut finish for a premium look or a light natural pine for an eco-friendly vibe, just send us a color swatch or Pantone code, and we&#8217;ll match it.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: 