in-node=\"38\">Wooden Kinetic Flip Photo Box<\/b>. This isn&#8217;t just a photo frame; it&#8217;s an interactive experience. By turning the brass handle on the side, the internal mechanism flips through a sequence of photos, creating a nostalgic animation effect. It is the perfect high-margin item for wedding planners, boutique gift shops, and corporate branding projects.<\/p>\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"20\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Why Choose Our Kinetic Boxes?<\/b><\/h4>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">1. Premium Craftsmanship (Not Cheap Plywood)<\/b> We use solid wood (North American Walnut or Maple) to ensure a luxurious tactile feel. The corners are finely sanded, and the surface is treated with natural wood wax oil, making it safe and durable. The brass components are anti-oxidation treated to ensure the crank works smoothly for years.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><b data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">2. The &#8220;Surprise&#8221; Element: LED Lighting<\/b> We&#8217;ve upgraded the traditional design by adding a warm LED light inside. When the handle is turned, the photos are illuminated from within, creating a romantic atmosphere\u2014especially popular for proposal gifts or memorial keepsakes.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">3. One-Stop Customization Service<\/b> You don&#8217;t need to worry about the technical side.<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"24\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"24,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Photo Printing:<\/b> Send us your client&#8217;s digital photos; we handle the high-definition printing and assembly.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"24,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Brand Engraving:<\/b> We can laser engrave your company logo or a special message on the wood surface.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"24,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Packaging:<\/b> We offer custom gift boxes with foam inserts to ensure the glass and mechanism are 100% safe during shipping.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">4. Factory Direct Benefits<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"26\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Competitive Pricing:<\/b> No middleman. We offer tiered pricing based on your volume.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Fast Turnaround:<\/b> Sample ready in 3-5 days; Mass production in 15-20 days.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Flexible MOQ:<\/b> We support small businesses. Start with a small batch to test your market response.<\/p>\n<h2 data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\">5. \ud83d\udcac FAQ<\/h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can the end-user change the photos themselves?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"50\">A:<\/b> Technically yes, but it requires some patience to assemble the mechanism. Most of our B2B clients prefer to send us the photos beforehand so we can deliver a ready-to-gift finished product. If you are a retailer, we can provide a &#8220;DIY Kit&#8221; version with instructions.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><b data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Does the LED light need to be plugged in?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><b data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">A:<\/b> No, that would be messy. It runs on a small button cell battery hidden inside the box, so it keeps the look clean and cordless. The battery is easy to replace.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: I sell on Amazon. is the packaging safe enough?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"51\">A:<\/b> Absolutely. We know how rough shipping can be. We use reinforced individual boxes with custom-cut foam padding to protect the glass window and the wooden gears. We can also label the boxes with your FBA barcodes for free.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I mix different wood colors in one order?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><b data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">A:<\/b> Yes! For an order of 100 units, for example, you can split it into 50 Walnut and 50 Maple. We want to help you test which color sells best in your shop.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5612\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13.png\" alt=\"wooden-kinetic-flip-photo-box-walnut\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13-600x600.png 600w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-13-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5611\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Photo-Frame-7.png\" alt=\"wooden-kinetic-flip-photo-box-walnut\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02