natives.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Maximized Capacity:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Lid:<\/b> Features built-in hooks and an elastic pouch specifically designed to keep necklaces tangle-free.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Top Tray:<\/b> Removable tray with specialized rolls for rings\/earrings and small grids for studs.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bottom Layer:<\/b> Spacious compartments perfect for larger statement pieces, watches, or sunglasses.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Soft Velvet Protection:<\/b> The interior is lined with premium anti-tarnish velvet (customizable colors: beige, grey, black) to ensure delicate gems remain pristine.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Gift-Ready Hardware:<\/b> Finished with high-quality gold-plated hinges and a secure lock. Comes with a decorative tassel key, making it an ideal choice for holiday gifts, wedding favors, or anniversary presents.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Why Source From Us?<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"28\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"28,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Factory Direct Pricing:<\/b> Cut out the middleman and get competitive rates for bulk orders.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"28,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Flexible Customization:<\/b> We can laser engrave your brand logo on the lid or hot-stamp it on the velvet lining.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"28,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Safe Shipping:<\/b> Each box is packed with reinforced foam corners and sturdy mailer boxes to pass drop tests, ensuring they arrive safely at your warehouse or your customer&#8217;s door.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>FAQ<\/h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I mix different wood colors in one carton?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"50\">A:<\/b> Absolutely! We know you want to test the market. For your first trial order, we allow mixing colors (e.g., Walnut and Cherry) within a master carton so you can see which one sells best.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><b data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Is the velvet lining color customizable?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><b data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">A:<\/b> Yes. The standard stock comes with the cream\/beige velvet shown in the photos because it&#8217;s the most popular. But if you want a signature look\u2014like emerald green or black velvet to match your brand\u2014we can do that for orders over 500 pcs.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><b data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: How do you pack these to prevent breakage? <\/b><b data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wood can be fragile.<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><b data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"67\">A:<\/b> We take packaging seriously. Each jewelry box is wrapped in EPE foam sheet, then placed in an individual inner box with Styrofoam corners. We usually pack 8-12 units in a thick, corrugated master carton. We regularly ship these to Amazon FBA centers with zero breakage issues.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><b data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can I add my logo?<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\">