 it is lightweight, stable, and suitable for large-scale production. The natural wood grain gives the coaster a clean and simple look that works well across different markets.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1179\" data-end=\"1274\">It is not designed as a decorative item, but as a practical product that can be used every day.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1279\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1320\">Solid wood structure, smooth finish<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1322\" data-end=\"1529\">Each coaster is cut from solid pine wood boards and carefully sanded. The surface feels smooth to the touch and helps protect tables from heat marks and moisture caused by hot drinks, tea, or cold beverages.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1673\">The thickness is balanced for daily use. It is sturdy enough for caf\u00e9s and hotels, while still light enough for retail packaging and shipping.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1675\" data-end=\"1678\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"1680\" data-end=\"1721\">Different shapes for different brands<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1723\" data-end=\"1929\">We currently offer several standard shapes, including round, square, and hexagon.<br data-start=\"1804\" data-end=\"1807\" \/>Many buyers choose different shapes to match their brand style or to build a small product series using the same material.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1931\" data-end=\"2026\">If you have specific size or thickness requirements, adjustments can be made during production.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2031\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2033\" data-end=\"2062\">Designed for repeated use<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2064\" data-end=\"2207\">This wooden coaster is intended for repeated, long-term use.<br data-start=\"2124\" data-end=\"2127\" \/>It can be wiped clean easily after use and does not require special maintenance.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2366\">Because of its simple structure and natural material, it is commonly supplied to caf\u00e9s, hotels, restaurants, and brands selling wooden tableware collections.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2368\" data-end=\"2371\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2373\" data-end=\"2404\">OEM and private label ready<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2406\" data-end=\"2486\">As a manufacturer, we mainly supply this product for wholesale and OEM projects.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2730\">Logo customization is available, most commonly by laser engraving, which keeps a clean and durable finish on the wood surface. Packaging is fully customized based on customer requirements, whether for bulk shipment or branded retail programs.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2732\" data-end=\"2735\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2737\" data-end=\"2764\">Who this product is for<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2766\" data-end=\"2809\">This pine wood coaster set is suitable for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2810\" data-end=\"2906\">\n<li data-start=\"2810\" data-end=\"2840\">\n<p data-start=\"2812\" data-end=\"2840\">Importers and distributors<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2841\" data-end=\"2856\">\n<p data-start=\"2843\" data-end=\"2856\">Wholesalers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2857\" data-end=\"2873\">\n<p data-start=\"2859\" data-end=\"2873\">Brand owners<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2874\" data-end=\"2906\">\n<p data-start=\"2876\" data-end=\"2906\">Gift and tableware companies<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2908\" data-end=\"3019\">We focus on stable supply, consistent quality, and long-term cooperation rather than single-piece retail sales.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2908\" data-end=\"3019\">\n<p data-start=\"2908\" data-end=\"3019\">\n<p data-start=\"2908\" data-end=\"3019\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5564\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/pine-wood-coaster-1.png\" alt=\"pine wood coaster\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/pine-wood-coaster-1.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/u