ed. Most clients choose laser engraving, as it works well with pine wood and keeps a clean look.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"3916\" data-end=\"3919\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"3921\" data-end=\"3963\">Is this suitable for caf\u00e9s or hotels<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3964\" data-end=\"4082\">Yes. This coaster is often supplied to caf\u00e9s, hotels, and restaurants. It is designed for daily use and easy cleaning.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4084\" data-end=\"4087\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"4089\" data-end=\"4131\">How do you usually pack the coasters<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4132\" data-end=\"4268\">Packaging is based on customer requirements. We support bulk packing for wholesale orders and customized packaging for branded projects.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"4270\" data-end=\"4273\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"4275\" data-end=\"4315\">Who is this product mainly sold to<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4316\" data-end=\"4449\">This product is mainly supplied to importers, wholesalers, distributors, and brand owners sourcing wooden coaster products in volume.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p data-start=\"447\" data-end=\"552\">Made from solid natural pine wood, this pine wood coaster set is designed for wholesale and OEM supply.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"559\" data-end=\"705\">It is a simple, practical wooden coaster solution for importers, distributors, and brands looking for stable quality and flexible customization.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"797\">Shape, size, logo, and packaging can all be adjusted based on different market needs<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5564,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[100],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-5563","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-wooden-coasters","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"shipping-taxable","11":"product-type-simple"},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"hr