baskets, offering both functionality and a clean, modern appearance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1466\" data-end=\"1519\">Solid Wood Top with Customizable Material Options<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1521\" data-end=\"1833\">The top shelf is made from solid wood, providing stable support for teapots, jars, mugs, or coffee accessories. Wood material options include paulownia wood, pine wood, or other solid wood types according to customer requirements. Surface finish and color can be customized to match different market preferences.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1835\" data-end=\"1883\">Strong Metal Frame with Mesh Storage Baskets<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1885\" data-end=\"2164\">The metal frame is constructed from iron with powder coating treatment to improve durability and corrosion resistance. The bottom mesh baskets allow easy sorting and visibility of tea bags and coffee items, making daily use more convenient while keeping the countertop organized.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2166\" data-end=\"2217\">Designed for Commercial and Retail Applications<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2219\" data-end=\"2509\">This wooden tea bag organizer is suitable for kitchen countertops, coffee stations, tea corners, office pantries, and retail display setups. Its open design supports both practical storage and product presentation, making it a popular choice for private label programs and gift collections.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2511\" data-end=\"2548\">OEM and ODM Manufacturing Support<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2550\" data-end=\"2859\">As a direct factory supplier, we provide OEM and ODM services including size customization, material selection, logo branding, and structure adjustment. This product can be developed into exclusive models for different brands and sales channels. Packaging can be customized according to customer requirements.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3591\" data-end=\"3620\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n<h3 data-start=\"3622\" data-end=\"3686\">1. What materials are used for this wooden tea bag organizer<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3687\" data-end=\"3856\">This product is made with a solid wood top and a metal frame with mesh baskets. Wood types such as paulownia wood or pine wood can be customized based on customer needs.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3858\" data-end=\"3919\">2. Is this tea bag organizer suitable for coffee stations<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3920\" data-end=\"4076\">Yes, the organizer is designed for both tea and coffee stations. It can store tea bags, coffee sachets, sugar packets, and small accessories on countertops.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"4078\" data-end=\"4125\">3. Can the size and structure be customized<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4126\" data-end=\"4270\">Yes, we support customization of size, basket layout, wood thickness, and overall structure. OEM and ODM services are available for bulk orders.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"4272\" data-end=\"4307\">4. Do you support logo branding<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4308\" data-end=\"4434\">Yes, logo branding can be applied through laser engraving, printing, or metal nameplates depending on the design requirements.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"4436\" data-end=\"4502\">5. Is this product suitable for retail or private label brands<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"4503\" data-end=\"4659\">This wooden tea bag organizer rack is suitable for brands, retailers, distributors, and gift suppliers looking for customizable countertop storage products.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2550\" data-end=\"2859\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5525\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/metal-wood-organiser-1.png\" alt=\"Wooden Tea Bag Organizer\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/metal-wood-organiser-1.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/metal-wood-organiser-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/metal-wood-organiser-1-150x150.png 150w