2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Key Features &amp; Benefits<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"23\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Pocket-Perfect Slim Profile:<\/b> With a height of just <b data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"51\">2.4cm (0.9 inches)<\/b>, this box is significantly thinner than traditional cubes. It fits effortlessly into a jacket breast pocket or tight jeans pocket, ensuring the ring stays safe and hidden.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dual Ring Capacity:<\/b> The interior features two perfectly spaced slots lined with premium velvet (available in Black, White, or Maroon). It securely holds a bridal set (engagement ring + wedding band) or the couple&#8217;s exchange rings together in one place.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Premium Craftsmanship:<\/b> Made from a single piece of high-grade <b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"62\">Walnut Wood<\/b>, ensuring the wood grain flows continuously from the lid to the base. The <b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"148\">barrel hinges<\/b> are hidden for a clean look, and strong <b data-path-to-node=\"23,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"202\">magnets<\/b> keep the lid snapped shut during movement.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"23,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Rotating Display Effect:<\/b> The unique horizontal layout creates a stunning panoramic view of the rings when opened, making it a favorite prop for wedding photographers capturing detail shots.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><b data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Specifications<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"25\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Item Name:<\/b> Slim Rectangular Double Ring Bearer Box<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dimensions:<\/b> 90mm (L) x 36mm (W) x 24mm (H)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wood Finish:<\/b> Natural Walnut Oil Finish (Eco-friendly)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Insert:<\/b> High-density foam covered in velvet<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,4,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"25,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Weight:<\/b> Approx. 35g<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><b data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">\u00a0Why Source From Xiamen Chic Homeware?<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none\">\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Customization Ready:<\/b> The flat, elongated top surface is the perfect canvas for <b data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"79\">laser engraving<\/b> names, dates, or wedding logos.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Photography Friendly:<\/b> The matte wood finish absorbs light beautifully, reducing glare for product photography.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"27,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bulk Availability:<\/b> Consistent quality and grain matching for large wholesale orders.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5473\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Slim-Wooden-Double-Ring-Box-2.png\" alt=\"Slim Wooden Double Ring Box\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Slim-Wood