em for home decor retailers and gift shops.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><b data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Key Features &amp; Benefits<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"30\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Massive Storage Capacity:<\/b> Equipped with <b data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"40\">5 pull-out drawers<\/b> of varying depths. The top drawers are compartmentalized for small items like rings and earrings, while the deeper bottom drawers hold watches, sunglasses, and bracelets.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tangle-Free Necklace Storage:<\/b> The <b data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"34\">two side swing doors<\/b> reveal hidden hooks tailored for hanging necklaces and chains. This vertical storage design prevents tangling and keeps chains in pristine condition.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Built-in Vanity Mirror:<\/b> The top lid opens to reveal a large glass mirror, allowing users to try on jewelry and apply makeup effortlessly.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"30,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Premium Protection:<\/b> Every compartment is lined with <b data-path-to-node=\"30,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"52\">high-quality soft velvet<\/b> (available in linen or black) to ensure jewelry remains scratch-free and dust-free.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><b data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Specifications<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"32\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Item Name:<\/b> Vintage 5-Drawer Wooden Jewelry Chest<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"32,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Material:<\/b> P