.).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Smooth Finish:<\/b> Polished to perfection with no sharp edges.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"17,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Secure Hardware:<\/b> Features a durable metal latch and hinges to keep the lid firmly closed.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><b data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Manufacturer Direct Services (OEM\/ODM)<\/b> <b data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"39\">Xiamen Chic Homeware<\/b> is your reliable partner for bulk orders and custom projects.<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"19\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Brand Your Way:<\/b> We offer professional laser engraving or silk-screen printing to add your company logo or custom text on the lid or front.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tailored Packaging:<\/b> From drop-tested mailer boxes for e-commerce safety to full-color gift boxes for retail shelves, we provide packaging solutions that protect your profit margins.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Global Supply:<\/b> Experienced in shipping to Amazon FBA and international warehouses with competitive factory pricing.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) about Our Bamboo Tea Boxes<\/b><\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: What material is used for your tea storage boxes?<\/b> A: We use <b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"63\">100% natural solid bamboo<\/b> for the box structure, which is more durable and eco-friendly than standard wood. The window is made of high-transparency acrylic (shatter-resistant) or real glass, depending on your requirement.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Can Xiamen Chic Homeware customize the logo for my brand?<\/b> A: Yes, we specialize in OEM\/ODM services. We can apply your logo using <b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"133\">Laser Engraving<\/b> (for a permanent, premium look) or <b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"184\">Silk Screen Printing<\/b> (for colorful logos). Please send us your AI or PDF file, and we will provide a digital mock-up for approval.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Is the packaging safe for international shipping (especially for Amazon FBA)?<\/b> A: Absolutely. We understand the risk of breakage. Our standard safety packaging includes bubble wrap and a reinforced inner carton. For Amazon sellers, we can provide <b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"249\">drop-tested mailer boxes<\/b> to ensure the product arrives in perfect condition without the need for repacking.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: What is the lead time for samples and bulk orders?<\/b> A:<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sample Lead Time:<\/b> 3-5 working days (7 days if custom logo is required).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Mass Production:<\/b> 25-35 days after deposit, depending on the order quantity.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Q: Why should I buy from Xiamen Chic Homeware instead of a trading company?<\/b> A: We are a direct manufacturer based in Xiamen, China. Dealing directly with us means you get the <b data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"175\">best factory p