 data-end=\"722\">Acacia Wood Stash Box<\/strong> is a high-end wooden storage solution designed for cannabis accessories, smoking kits, and lifestyle gift markets.<br data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"840\" \/>Made from <strong data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"876\">100% solid acacia wood<\/strong>, it combines durability, rich natural grain, and luxury presentation \u2014 ideal for premium retail and private-label brands.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1000\" data-end=\"1217\">The box features a <strong data-start=\"1019\" data-end=\"1036\">built-in lock<\/strong>, a <strong data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1075\">removable wooden organizer tray<\/strong>, and multiple accessory compartments, allowing users to neatly store grinders, jars, rolling tools, and personal items in one compact system.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1219\" data-end=\"1222\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1240\">Key Features<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"1242\" data-end=\"1995\">\n<li data-start=\"1242\" data-end=\"1402\">\n<p data-start=\"1244\" data-end=\"1402\"><strong data-start=\"1244\" data-end=\"1278\">Solid Acacia Wood Construction<\/strong><br data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1281\" \/>Made from selected acacia hardwood, kiln-dried and polished for strength, moisture resistance, and long-term stability.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1404\" data-end=\"1574\">\n<p data-start=\"1406\" data-end=\"1574\"><strong data-start=\"1406\" data-end=\"1446\">Built-in Lock for Privacy &amp; Security<\/strong><br data-start=\"1446\" data-end=\"1449\" \/>Integrated lock keeps contents discreet and secure \u2014 a key requirement for cannabis, herbal, and lifestyle storage markets.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1731\">\n<p data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1731\"><strong data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1606\">Removable Organizer Tray<\/strong><br data-start=\"1606\" data-end=\"1609\" \/>The top tray lifts out, allowing flexible storage of larger items below while keeping daily-use tools easily accessible.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1862\">\n<p data-start=\"1735\" data-end=\"1862\"><strong data-start=\"1735\" data-end=\"1760\">Full Accessory Layout<\/strong><br data-start=\"1760\" data-end=\"1763\" \/>Designed to hold grinders, jars, rolling papers, brushes, and tools in a clean, organized layout.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1864\" data-end=\"1995\">\n<p data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1995\"><strong data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1895\">Premium Gift-Ready Design<\/strong><br data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1898\" \/>Natural wood texture and precision CNC cutting give this box a high-end, gift-grade appearance.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1997\" data-end=\"2000\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2002\" data-end=\"2015\">Ideal For<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2017\" data-end=\"2189\">\n<li data-start=\"2017\" data-end=\"2056\">\n<p data-start=\"2019\" data-end=\"2056\">Cannabis &amp; smoking accessory brands<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2057\" data-end=\"2085\">\n<p data-start=\"2059\" data-end=\"2085\">Lifestyle gift retailers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2086\" data-end=\"2116\">\n<p data-start=\"2088\" data-end=\"2116\">Subscription box companies<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2117\" data-end=\"2149\">\n<p data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2149\">Private label &amp; OEM programs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2150\" data-end=\"2189\">\n<p data-start=\"2152\" data-end=\"2189\">Online sellers (Amazon, Shopify, DTC)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2191\" data-end=\"2194\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2196\" data-end=\"2227\">OEM &amp; Customization Options<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2229\" data-end=\"2298\">As a <strong data-start=\"2234\" data-end=\"2266\">direct manufacturer in China<\/strong>, we support full customization:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2300\" data-end=\"2469\">\n<li data-start=\"2300\" data-end=\"2323\">\n<p data-start=\"2302\" data-end=\"2323\">Laser-engraved logo<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2361\">\n<p data-start=\"2326\" data-end=\"2361\">Custom box size &amp; internal layout<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2362\" data-end=\"2399\">\n<p data-start=\"2364\" data-end=\"2399\">Custom color box \/ gift packaging<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2433\">\n<p data-start=\"2402\" data-end=\"2433\">Hardware &amp; lock style options<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2434\" data-end=\"2469\">\n<p data-start=\"2436\" data-end=\"2469\">Bulk &amp; private label production<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2471\" data-end=\"2506\">Low MOQ available for brand trials.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2511\" \/>\n<h3 data-start=\"2513\" data-end=\"2541\">Material &amp; Craftsmanship<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2543\" data-end=\"2753\">\n<li data-start=\"2543\" data-end=\"2579\">\n<p data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2579\">Material: 100% Solid Acacia Wood<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2580\" data-end=\"2635\">\n<p data-start=\"2582\" data-end=\"2635\">Finish: Smooth sanded, natural oil or clear coating<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2636\" data-end=\"2688\">\n<p data-start=\"2638\" data-end=\"2688\">Construction: CNC-cut panels + reinforced joints<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2689\" data-end=\"2753\">\n<p data-start=\"2691\" data-end=\"2753\">Moisture control: Kiln-dried to prevent warping and cracking<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2755\" data-end=\"2758\" \/>\n<p data-start=\"2760\" data-end=\"2967\">If you are looking for a <strong data-start=\"2785\" data-end=\"2826\">high-margin, premium wooden stash box<\/strong> to build your brand or expand your product line, this acacia wood model offers both strong retail appeal and reliable factory-level quality.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2760\" data-end=\"2967\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5395\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/acacia-wood-stash-box-6.png\" alt=\"wooden stash box\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmch