ing look delicious.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,1\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The Ultimate Pizza Companion<\/b> With a generous <b data-path-to-node=\"11,1\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">33.5 cm (approx. 13.2&#8243;) diameter<\/b>, this board is the perfect size for a standard 12-inch pizza. The sturdy handle lets you securely carry hot food from the counter to the dining table with ease.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,2\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Designed for Display<\/b> Why hide your cutting board in a drawer? The distinctive <b data-path-to-node=\"11,2\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">circular handle design<\/b> not only offers a comfortable grip but also allows you to hang the board on a kitchen wall hook. The warm, natural wood tones add a cozy, farmhouse aesthetic to your kitchen decor when not in use.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,3\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Durable &amp; Natural<\/b> Made from 100% natural Acacia wood, this board is naturally resistant to water and scratches. It\u2019s built to last for years of slicing, dicing, and serving.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,4\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dimensions:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11,5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,5,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Diameter:<\/b> 33.5 cm (13.2 inches)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,5,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Total Length (with handle):<\/b> 44 cm (17.3 inches)<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5255\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/round-cutting-board-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/round-cutting-board-1.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/roun