-to-node=\"10,0\" data-index-in-node=\"144\">storage stand<\/b>. Unlike traditional boards that clutter your drawers or lean awkwardly against the wall, this set stands proudly on your countertop, doubling as a piece of rustic decor.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,1\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-2\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,1\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Air-Dry &amp; Space-Saving Solution<\/b> The included wooden stand isn&#8217;t just for looks\u2014it\u2019s practical. By storing the boards vertically, it ensures proper airflow for <b data-path-to-node=\"10,1\" data-index-in-node=\"159\">quick and hygienic air drying<\/b> after washing. It keeps your boards accessible yet neatly tucked away, saving valuable counter space.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,2\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-3\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Three Sizes, Limitless Uses<\/b> Prepared for any recipe, this set includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"10,3\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,3,0,0\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-4\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Large (16&#8243; x 12&#8243;):<\/b> Perfect for slicing roasts, poultry, or large watermelons.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,3,1,0\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-5\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Medium (14&#8243; x 10&#8243;):<\/b> Ideal for chopping vegetables and everyday meal prep.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,3,2,0\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-6\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Small (12&#8243; x 8&#8243;):<\/b> Great for slicing cheese, lemons, or serving small appetizers.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,4\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-7\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Durable &amp; Functional<\/b> Made from high-quality <b data-path-to-node=\"10,4\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">Acacia wood<\/b> (0.8&#8243; thick), these boards are tough on food but gentle on knives. The <b data-path-to-node=\"10,4\" data-index-in-node=\"127\">ergonomic handle cutout<\/b> makes it easy to grab a board and go, or to serve guests directly at the dining table.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,5\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-8\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Care Instructions:<\/b> Hand wash with mild soap and water. Dry thoroughly before placing in the stand. Periodically apply mineral oil to maintain the wood&#8217;s finish.<\/p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,5\" data-rm-block-id=\"block-9\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5248\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1-600x600.png 600w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-1-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5249\" src=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-2.png 900w, https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Acacia-Cutting-Board-Set-with-Stand-2-300x300.pn