ified_gmt":"2026-01-17T06:16:10","slug":"expandable-bamboo-spice-rack","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/xmchichomeware.com\/product\/expandable-bamboo-spice-rack\/","title":{"rendered":"Expandable Bamboo Spice Rack Shelf"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3 data-start=\"183\" data-end=\"244\">Manufacturer-Direct Bamboo Spice Rack for Wholesale &amp; OEM<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"246\" data-end=\"541\">This <strong data-start=\"251\" data-end=\"283\">expandable bamboo spice rack<\/strong> is manufactured in China by a professional bamboo kitchenware factory. Designed for brands, retailers, and distributors, it offers a flexible and space-saving solution for organizing spice jars and small containers on kitchen countertops or inside cabinets.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"543\" data-end=\"586\">Adjustable Width for Flexible Storage<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"837\">The telescopic design allows the spice rack to expand from <strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"674\">8.75 inches to 15 inches<\/strong>, making it easy to adapt to different countertop or cabinet widths. This adjustable structure helps maximize available space while keeping spices neatly arranged.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"839\" data-end=\"879\">Tiered Step Design for Easy Access<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"1125\">The stepped, multi-level layout improves visibility and access to spice jars, allowing users to quickly identify and reach items without moving others. This design is ideal for daily cooking environments where efficiency and organization matter.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1127\" data-end=\"1160\">Natural Bamboo Construction<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1406\">Made from selected natural bamboo, this spice rack offers stable structure, moisture resistance, and a smooth surface finish. The material is suitable for long-term kitchen use and easy to clean, supporting consistent quality in bulk production.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1408\" data-end=\"1447\">Designed for Bra